#. type: Content of: <div><div><div><span><p>
#: _includes/spring-userstory-callout.html:9
#, fuzzy
msgid "First, they realized that migrating from Spring Boot to a CDI-based framework didn't require a lot of effort for their Spring developers, resulting in a small learning curve... with Quarkus they saw a '30 to 40% better developer productivity vis-a-vis Spring Boot, and this is for an ex-Spring Boot developer', according to Christos."
msgstr "首先，他们意识到，对于Spring开发人员而言，从Spring Boot迁移到基于CDI的框架并不需要付出太多努力，因此学习曲线很平缓…… 据克里斯托斯（Christos）介绍，使用 Quarkus 后，他们发现“与 Spring Boot 相比，开发人员的生产力提高了 30% 至 40%，而这还是针对一位前 Spring Boot 开发人员而言”。"

